balsa: balsa (GNOME light weight email client)
balsa:
balsa: Balsa is an e-mail client for GNOME, highly configurable and
balsa: incorporating all the features you would expect in a robust mail
balsa: client. It supports local mailbox formats mbox, maildir, mh, nested 
balsa: mailboxes, multi-threaded mail retrevial, MIME support, SMTP and/or 
balsa: use of local MTA, and GPG/OpenPGP.
